data.description: Exquisite 3-bdr, 3.5-bth David Weekley Homes residence boasts unparalleled craftsmanship and a host of upgraded features that redefine luxury living. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by a thoughtfully designed interior. Custom upgrades include a spacious primary walk-in closet, wallpaper, surround sound, sliding glass doors, turfed backyard, hardware, light fixtures, mirrors, ring camera doorbell, electric shades, window treatments, & fireplace. The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, equipped with top-tier appliances, custom cabinets and marble countertops. The additional two bedrooms offer generous space. Enjoy two bonus spaces, ideal for a home gym, playroom, or whatever suits your lifestyle, as well as a dedicated office. 10-yr structural warranty seamlessly transfers to the new owner. As a bonus, residents can enjoy the  community pool.
